                        <a class="Link" href="https://www.latimes.com/bestcovery/best-wireless-router-overall" aria-label="Keep Your Internet Buffer-Free With The Best Wireless Router">
    <img class="Image" alt="best wireless routers" width="840" height="560"
        data-src="https://cdn.bestcovery.ca-times-dam.psdops.com/dims4/default/5b3bcb2/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1500x1000+0+250/resize/840x560!/quality/90/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fbestcovery-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F62%2F8d%2Fbbadcadb142f40953d99fdd18b5b%2Fnetgear-r7800.jpg" data-lazy-load="true" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==">

